          "effect": "You swing the weapon in an arc, causing a spray of paint of a color of your choice (chosen from black, blue, green, orange, white, or yellow) to splatter all creatures in a 30-foot cone. Each creature takes 14d6 energy damage based on the color of the paint (void for black, cold for blue, acid for green, fire for orange, vitality for white, or electricity for yellow) and must attempt a DC 34 Reflex save.",
